* Pierre Stone (me): Was present for all meetings, feels like I was the leader. Kept track of deliverables and wrote a major section of the report -> 7
* Oleana Root: Pretty good, tried hard to help and was reliable. Good worker -> 5
* Ronin Oscar: My partner who was as reliable and had a lot of key ideas. Figured out the pricing model and did a great job on the mockup -> 4
